{"article_id":"UhEfR4tZOxgOXxfx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republican leaders in the House and Senate will face restless rank-and-file members Tuesday morning","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"when they give updates on ongoing negotiations","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to cobble together a budget plan","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that would end a two-week-old partial government shutdown","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and increase the U.S. debt ceiling .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky. , and Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid , D-Nev. , scrambled late Monday","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"to iron out the specifics of an emerging budget proposal","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"after a string of prior plans fizzled .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Reid appeared on the chamber floor Monday night","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"to announce ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"`` We 've made tremendous progress","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"-- we are not there yet --","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"but tremendous progress ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"and everyone just needs to be patient . ''","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"McConnell added ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"`` We 've had a good day ...","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"it 's safe to say","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"we 've made substantial progress","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"and we look forward to making more progress in the near future . ''","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The House GOP Conference is scheduled to meet at 9 a.m.","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"to discuss the tentative framework of the budget proposal with members ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"many of whom cast a skeptical eye toward the details of the negotiations","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that were dripping out Monday night .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"The Senate Republican Conference is scheduled to meet at 11 a.m.","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"to receive an update on negotiations .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"Resistance in the House could scuttle , or at least stall , anything","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"that emerges from the Senate .","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"The White House abruptly postponed a meeting with congressional leaders","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"set for Monday afternoon ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"to give senators space","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"to work .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"`` We 're going to get this done , ''","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Sen. Joe Manchin , D-W.Va. , claimed .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"It 's unclear whether the optimism would be matched by results .","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"After several prior plans fell apart over the weekend ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"lawmakers are working on a tight timeframe .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Congress ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"aside from grappling with the partial government shutdown ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"faces an Oct. 17 deadline","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"to raise the debt ceiling .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"After that date ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"the Treasury Department warns ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"the U.S. government will not be able to pay all its bills .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Fox News has learned","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that the emerging framework would raise the debt ceiling through February ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"and include a spending bill","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"meant to last through Jan. 15 .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Importantly , a tentative provision","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to repeal or delay the medical device tax in ObamaCare","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"has been taken out ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"a senior Democratic aide said .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"But the proposal could include other modest items","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"pertaining to ObamaCare ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"including income verification for those","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"getting subsidies","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and a one-year delay of at least one obscure fee","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"which had been sought by unions .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"House Republicans are watching the negotiations play out ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"according to sources","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"still want to see provisions","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"to strip ObamaCare subsidies for congressional staff .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"It 's unclear where they will ultimately fall ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"but conservative members predicted a `` huge fight ''","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"if McConnell `` completely capitulates . ''","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Negotiators are still tinkering with the framework ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"and the details could change .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Asked earlier Monday","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"if they were closer to a deal ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Reid said :","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"`` I hope so . ``","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"A McConnell spokesman said","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"the two were `` engaged in good faith negotiations","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"and those talks will continue . ''","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"The new framework appears to be driven largely by Senate Democrats , but potentially with buy-in from McConnell .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Pressure is mounting from all sides","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"to reach an agreement .","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"There is fear","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"that the financial markets could start to dive","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"if traders lose confidence","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that a deal will ultimately emerge .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"And furloughed federal workers ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"now entering week three of the partial shutdown ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"are just now starting to see the hit to their paychecks .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"But both sides of the debate were having a difficult time","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"keeping track of what the other wants out of a deal .","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"A standoff","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"that began as a fight by Republicans","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"to unravel ObamaCare","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"is now largely a fight over spending levels","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"-- which has emerged as a major sticking point .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"After a string of budget proposals fell apart over the weekend ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"GOP lawmakers on Sunday pointedly accused Democrats of trying to squeeze Republicans to roll back across-the-board spending cuts","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"known as sequester .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"`` I agree","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"that Republicans started with the overreach ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"but now Democrats are one tick too cute , ''","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"Sen. Bob Corker , R-Tenn. , told `` Fox News Sunday .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"'' `` They are now overreaching . ''","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"`` both sides need to come to the middle of the road . ''","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"A prior plan ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"fronted by Sen. Susan Collins , R-Maine ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"would have funded the government for six months ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"raised the debt limit through Jan. 31 ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"and delayed the health care law 's medical device tax .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"As Reid dismissed the plan on Saturday ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"the dispute over spending levels escalated .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Republicans want to continue current spending at $ 986.7 billion","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"and leave untouched the new round of cuts on Jan. 15","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"that would reduce the amount to $ 967 billion .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Democrats , though , want to figure out a way","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"to undo the reductions ,","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"plus enact a long-term extension of the debt limit increase and a short-term spending bill","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"to reopen the government .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"Republicans bristled at Democrats ' demands .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"A House Republican leadership aide said Sunday","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"that Reid `` moved the goalposts ''","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"by trying to `` violate '' spending levels","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"set in the 2011 Budget Control Act .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"But Democrats denied","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"they were trying to violate those levels .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"A Senate Democratic leadership aide said","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"`` the suggestion","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"that Democrats insist on breaking the budget caps","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"is false","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"and belied by the facts . ''","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"Essentially , Democrats argue","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"that they would accept current spending levels for a short period","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"-- just not as long","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"as Collins proposed --","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"so they can have another go at the sequester cuts in the near future .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Congressional sources confirmed to Fox News","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"that the talks between Reid and McConnell are focusing on the length of the spending bill versus the length of the debt-ceiling increase .","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"Reid wants a longer extension on the debt ceiling , but a shorter-term spending bill .","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"Unclear was whether any Senate deal would pass the Republican-controlled House by Thursday ,","depth":5},{"id":137,"text":"though Senate Democrats were hoping","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"momentum and the debt-ceiling deadline would pressure House lawmakers .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":277,"left":173,"right":276,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":164,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":158,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":143,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":0,"right":142,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":1,"right":141,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":2,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":145,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":144,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":150,"right":155,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":8,"right":149,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":9,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":146,"right":12,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":151,"right":154,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":19,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":16,"right":152,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":163,"left":161,"right":162,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":20,"right":160,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"paren